Sales and Business Development Executive Job
Posted: 3 days ago
We are a Premiere Lighting Company based in Dubai specializing in Project sales. We have a very good reputation in the market, have executed several reputed projects across the ME and represent some very good International Brands exclusively. We are a professionally run company comprising of very experienced and enthusiastic Engineers and technicians.
We are currently seeking to hire the services of a seasoned Sales/Marketing Executive with proven experience in Project Sales. We require the Executive to work for us on an attractive and fair Profit Sharing/ Commission basis.
A thorough understanding and experience of Lighting sales with excellent contacts for Projects in UAE is an absolute must for the right candidate. We shall provide you with all the technical and other back office support required continuously.
Please be assured that your application shall be kept strictly confidential. Interested applicants can forward their profiles to Human Resources @PLSUAE.COM
